caption.p: Effect of Cardamom oil on acetylcholinesterase assay in (A) hippocampus and (B) cortex tissue in AlCl 3-induced neurotoxicity in rats. Data are expressed as mean Â± SEM ( n = 6), ##p < 0.01, ### p < 0.001 when compared with normal control, *** p < 0.001, ** p < 0.01, * p < 0.05 when compared with disease control group.
